.000Z","msg":"明朝滅亡就已經收咗皮<br />\n<br />\n維基啲嘢當參考下，鬼佬喺明朝後期入嚟傳教就順便將知識帶埋俾中國人，亦都有唔少人將學到嘅嘢寫書流入民間<br />\n<br />\n康熙雍正一樣有跟鬼佬學西方知識，但民間好似冇乜<br />\n<br />\n好多人都成日講中國人做嘢冇鬼佬咁嚴謹認真，啟蒙時代之前嘅鬼佬同中國人其實都係差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/明朝科技\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E6%98%8E%E6%9C%9D%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DO2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=4273aef5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/明朝科技</a>"},{"pid":"1668a638abaef23e877af8b480c90da9b21431a7","tid":2486471,"uid":181156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T04:24:21.000Z","msg":"屌憎支共都咪撚吹捧晚清呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e1d9220c974f2dbf0d12a090863c38a6bce83c8","tid":2486471,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1668a638abaef23e877af8b480c90da9b21431a7","tid":2486471,"uid":181156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T04:24:21.000Z","msg":"屌憎支共都咪撚吹捧晚清呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T04:30:23.000Z","msg":"支持滿清政府合法施政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec9dfc4c37e9af6e1523e681d43ebeec7e5f99d3","tid":2486471,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T04:32:03.000Z","msg":"支持恢復帝制"},{"pid":"70572e6ca08c154c772fe7303430e4362721bf8f","tid":2486471,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T05:31:13.000Z","msg":"中國喺1911年之前只係地理名詞，嗰度嘅人亦非整體。"},{"pid":"0c417a1b0ef7722cf858b8b6156d8ab08e2870fd","tid":2486471,"uid":282118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T05:36:59.000Z","msg":"曾經出現過戌戍變法、自立軍起義<br />\n可惜都係失敗咗<br />\n都算係清末最貼近世界嘅一次改革<br />\n<br />\n反清革命做到嘅嘢其實只係得推翻宣統皇帝<br />\n民族民權民生都冇一樣做到"},{"pid":"6a679f6da4de8f0c8f0443382b